StructureDefinition: CareConnect-Patient-1

The official URL for this profile is: 

https://hl7.org.uk/fhir/StructureDefinition/CareConnect-Patient-1

This profile defines a patient administration details structure that includes core localisation concepts for use in a UK context.

Identifiers

These definitions represent common data held in the Patient.identifier element:

  • NHS Number - England and Wales
  • CHI Number - Scotland. Not yet specified
  • HSNi - Northern Ireland. Not yet specified

Examples

Patient with NHS Number and NHS Trust Identifier
